      <div class="msgContentFrame">Having started my DoH with the release of CE, I have decided to start my first DoW and set my mind on a lancer.  <br />What I need info with is lancer's party behavior with skills and attacks. Like what skills and abilities do you use in battle. Do you just spam attacks. Thanks for any info. <br /> <br /><i><span class="sm">Edited, Nov 18th 2010  3:35pm by Keele </span></i><div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div><img src="http://common.zam.com/xivsigs/1805180.png" height="144" width="482" alt="Signature Image" border="0" /> <br /></div></div>
