othing we can do about it until SE scraps the SP system and brings sanity to grouping. <br /> <br /> <br /><i><span class="sm">Edited, Nov  7th 2010  7:30am by Omena </span></i> <br /> <br /><i><span class="sm">Edited, Nov  7th 2010  7:30am by Omena </span></i></div>
