e attacks have low SP gain damage based, you're actually gimping your SP gain by doing it again and again. Furthermore, you have to take the time you took to kill a mob into consideration, it is never a good idea to have a long fight when the SP cap stays at 500, you need to balance between SP gain per kill and time you took to kill it, more damage and less Stamina cost equals to faster kill yes? Unless somehow the mob died from your Bind instead of damage. <br /> <br /> <br /><i><span class="sm">Edited, Nov  8th 2010  6:02pm by Khornette </span></i> <br /> <br /><i><span class="sm">Edited, Nov  8th 2010  7:30pm by Khornette </span></i><div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div><img src="http://common.zam.com/xivsigs/1807831.png" height="144" width="482" alt="Signature Image" border="0" /></div></div>
